, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/pinkpantheress-kendrick-lamar-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/pinkpantheress-kendrick-lamar-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/pinkpantheress-kendrick-lamar-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pinkpantheress">PinkPantheress</a>透露，由于手机处于静音状态，她错过了在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 的</a>歌曲中亮相的机会。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/pinkpantheress-cover-interview-2023-take-me-home-ep-3390837">PinkPantheress：“我不关心节拍，我关心笔”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位英国创作歌手在一次新的采访中解释说，她错过了与这位“Humble”说唱歌手的录音室会议，因为她正在电影院约会，所以她错过了通知。</p><p> “我并不是想约会，尽管我喜欢约会，”她告诉<a href="https://i-d.vice.com/en/article/88xkva/pinkpantheress-interview-heaven-knows" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《iD》</em>杂志</a>。她接着分享了她如何“差点”与拉马尔一起出演一首歌曲，但在她的约会对象要求她在电影期间将手机调成静音后，她错过了录音室会议。</p><p> “哦，操，我什至无法思考，”她说。 “我和这个家伙一起看<em>《夜行者</em>》。”</p><p> PinkPantheress 与多位艺术家合作制作了多部作品， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pinkpantheress-on-her-boys-a-liar-pt-2-collaboration-with-ice-spice-once-you-see-the-world-she-embodies-it-makes-you-view-the-music-differently-3393178">其中包括在她的单曲《Boy&#39;s a liar》中招募 Ice Spice</a> 。她还与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stray-kids">Stray Kids</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hyunjin">Hyunjin</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/troye-sivan-rush-remix-stray-kids-hyunjin-pinkpantheress-3490667">参与了 Troye Sivan 的“Rush”的混音</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3391511" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3391511" style="width: 2560px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3391511" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/NME-HERO-PinkPantheress@2560x1625.jpg" alt="粉红豹" width="2560" height="1625" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/NME-HERO-PinkPantheress@2560x1625.jpg 2560w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/NME-HERO-PinkPantheress@2560x1625-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/NME-HERO-PinkPantheress@2560x1625-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/NME-HERO-PinkPantheress@2560x1625-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/NME-HERO-PinkPantheress@2560x1625-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/NME-HERO-PinkPantheress@2560x1625-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3391511" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：查理·布劳恩</figcaption></figure><p>上个月，这位歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pinkpantheress-announces-debut-album-heaven-knows-and-shares-uk-and-eu-tour-dates-3514069">宣布了她的首张唱片《Heaven Knows》，并分享了明年英国和欧盟的巡演日期</a>。</p><p>据新闻稿称，《天知道》揭示了歌手探索各种类型的关系时的内心自我反思，包括浪漫、准社会、物质追求、悲伤以及在孤独中寻找满足。</p><p>在一份新闻声明中谈到这张唱片时，这位歌手说：“这张唱片是关于失去亲人的悲伤，但在孤独中与自己相处。从地狱到炼狱的旅程，但我对在那里很满意。”</p><p>在宣布专辑之前，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pinkpantheress-drops-ethereal-track-mosquito-music-video-3507820">歌手分享了新单曲“Mosquito”</a> ，并发布了随附的音乐视频。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pinkpantheress-missed-studio-session-with-kendrick-lamar-because-phone-was-silent-3531995">PinkPantheress 因为手机静音而错过了与 Kendrick Lamar 的录音室会议的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
